1
00:00:45,439 --> 00:00:46,359
Zhou Xingbang

2
00:00:57,759 --> 00:00:58,479
Chuanzhong

3
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:00,759
You could've just come.

4
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:02,000
Why bring all this stuff?

5
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:04,680
If I came to see you

6
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,280
empty-handed,

7
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,760
wouldn't you scold me?

8
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:08,719
I mean,

9
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,760
what brings you here today?

10
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:11,920
What?

11
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,840
Only dead men can visit you?

12
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,719
No, no.

13
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,719
Of course not.

14
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,239
Ruling,

15
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,719
bring some tea.

16
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:23,560
Lao Jiugui,

17
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,799
no wonder

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,840
you refused that mansion I offered.

19
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:29,760
Turns out you've got beautiful scenery,

20
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,200
a real paradise here.

21
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:35,120
Not as grand as you.

22
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,480
Ruling,

23
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,040
this man

24
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,079
is Dongsheng's superior,

25
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,519
Li Chuanzhong.

26
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:44,120
Brigade Commander Li.

27
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,840
Now,

28
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,200
he's a Division Commander.

29
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:52,280
Forgive my ignorance,

30
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,920
Division Commander Li.

31
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:55,599
A pleasure, truly a pleasure.

32
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:58,480
My old drunkard often tells me

33
00:01:58,719 --> 00:02:00,879
about your army days together.

34
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,439
You told the kid about that?

35
00:02:04,879 --> 00:02:07,920
Haven't seen my dear niece in ten years,

36
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:09,439
and look how she's grown!

37
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,960
Clearly she doesn't take after you.

38
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:14,879
No, no.

39
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,159
No.

40
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:16,879
Well,

41
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:17,840
Commander,

42
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,199
I'm

43
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,759
his wife.

44
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,039
Oh, Lao Jiugui, Lao Jiugui...

45
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,240
No, wait.

46
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:31,960
You're not Lao Jiugui.

47
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,400
You're Old Goat.

48
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:36,599
How did I become Old Goat now?

49
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,000
An old goat

50
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:39,319
robbing the cradle.

51
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,199
How embarrassing!

52
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,840
Please excuse us, Commander.

53
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:50,360
How come I don't see our Dongsheng?

54
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,520
Well,

55
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,400
I came here

56
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:57,879
firstly,

57
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,520
to visit Lao Jiugui.

58
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,199
And secondly,

59
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:05,919
to ask him to come see Dongsheng.

60
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,599
Dongsheng,

61
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:09,840
what's wrong with him?

62
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:12,680
You,

63
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:14,599
why so nervous?

64
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,800
What could happen to him?

65
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,120
He's fine,

66
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,319
perfectly fine.

67
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:21,360
He just can't come over right now,

68
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,039
so we need

69
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,960
you to go see him.

70
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:29,439
Oh come on,

71
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:32,520
you could've just sent someone for that.

72
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,719
Look at all this fuss you're making.

73
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:37,439
Mainly, I wanted to see you too.

74
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,639
Then I'll go with Chuanzhong.

75
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,800
Let's go, let's go.

76
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,520
Come on, come on.

77
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,439
So impatient.

78
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,319
Goodbye, Sis.

79
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,120
Let's go.

80
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:51,439
Go.

81
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,080
Division Commander.

82
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,240
Everything's ready.

83
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,120
Lao Jiugui.

84
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,560
After you.

85
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,240
I know this place well.

86
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,080
Come on, let's go.

87
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,000
After you, Lao Jiugui.

88
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,959
Bring him in.

89
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,360
Master.

90
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,759
What are you doing here?

91
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:37,959
What's all this about?

92
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,639
Did you mess up?

93
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:46,480
Is that it?

94
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,519
Made your Division Commander angry?

95
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,160
Is that it?

96
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:50,720
Speak up!

97
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,199
Out with it!

98
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,160
Come on, quick.

99
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,519
Apologize to the Division Commander.

100
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:55,800
Hurry up and speak.

101
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,079
Master...

102
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,360
What is it? Tell me.

103
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,079
Master, please don't ask.

104
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,759
Zhou Xingbang betrayed us.

105
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,600
Zhou Xingbang betrayed us.

106
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,360
That's no big deal.

107
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,000
Right?

108
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,160
Not a big deal at all.

109
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,000
If Zhou Xingbang betrayed you,

110
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,839
you should go after his parents.

111
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,199
It's got nothing to do with my disciple.

112
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,759
It's fine, let's go.

113
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:22,800
Lao Jiugui.

114
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,240
Quit the act.

115
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,480
We've known each other for over ten years.

116
00:05:34,519 --> 00:05:35,160
No more pretending.

117
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,000
Enough pretending.

118
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,000
Speak.

119
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,560
What are your terms

120
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,920
to let Dongsheng go?

121
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,160
Straight to the point.

122
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,480
Lao Jiugui,

123
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:59,480
my demand is simple.

124
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:01,360
As long as

125
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:02,920
you use the Ghost Soldiers

126
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,600
to help me defeat the Guerrilla forces,

127
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,199
once it's done,

128
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,360
Dongsheng

129
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,839
will be returned to you unharmed.

130
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:10,319
Fine.

131
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,160
No problem.

132
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:12,759
No problem.

133
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,600
Master.

134
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:14,720
Master, don't!

135
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:15,680
You can't abet the wicked.

136
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,120
Master!

137
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:17,240
Master, then you...

138
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:19,480
Take him away.

139
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,519
Master!

140
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,639
Master!

141
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,639
Master!

142
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:23,879
Master!

143
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,839
Take good care of Dongsheng.

144
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,519
When do we set out?

145
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,040
Early tomorrow morning.

146
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,160
I'll head back and get ready.

147
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:44,199
Now what?

148
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,040
Lao Jiugui,

149
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,639
you've served in the military too.

150
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,680
For a military operation,

151
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:57,279
secrecy must be maintained.

152
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,439
Whatever you need,

153
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,720
write it down.

154
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,000
I'll

155
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,680
send someone to fetch it.

156
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,879
When will Lao Jiugui and Dongsheng be back?

157
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,680
Stop dawdling.

158
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,319
If you want to see them again,

159
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,680
prepare what's on the list.

160
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,759
Wait here.

161
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,600
When are they coming back?

162
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,279
Don't worry.

163
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,920
They'll come back sooner or later.

164
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,480
Because

165
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:09,160
isn't the Bone-Keeping Temple where the dead are stored?

166
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:11,279
What did you say?

167
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:41,480
Oh no.

168
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,399
Stop.

169
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,279
What's wrong?

170
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,200
I need to take a dump.

171
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,159
Take a dump?

172
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,879
If you don't trust me, come along.

173
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,240
What's there not to trust?

174
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:08,639
They say master and disciple are like father and son.

175
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:11,919
Would Lao Jiugui ditch his own disciple?

176
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:13,720
Go on.

177
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,759
Don't soil your pants.

178
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,559
Hurry up.

179
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,559
What kind of soup is this?

180
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:31,360
Let me, let me.

181
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,639
Wild greens and mushroom soup.

182
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,039
Is it ready?

183
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,200
Yes, it's ready.

184
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,399
Serve the soup.

185
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:39,120
Serving up.

186
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,480
Come on, come on.

187
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,559
Everyone, time to eat!

188
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,919
Come, come.

189
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:51,480
I'm really starving.

190
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,200
Xingbang.

191
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,600
Is the Division Commander's meal that hot to handle?

192
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,679
Division Commander.

193
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,559
The Guerrillas' camp

194
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,080
is right over there.

195
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,679
Lao Jiugui,

196
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,399
the rest is up to you.

197
00:10:53,399 --> 00:10:55,759
Given our ten years of friendship,

198
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:58,120
I always keep my word.

199
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,759
As long as you summon the Five Fury Troops

200
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,200
to wipe out those Guerrillas over there,

201
00:11:03,799 --> 00:11:06,399
I guarantee your disciple's safety.

202
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:08,240
As for the past,

203
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,879
I'll let bygones be bygones.

204
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:19,240
Then set up the Ritual Altar over there.

205
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:21,919
Alright.

206
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:23,519
Jing Chang.

207
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,120
Yes, sir.

208
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:28,279
Do as Lao Jiugui says.

209
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:28,960
Yes, sir.

210
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:36,360
I'm starting then.

211
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:37,600
Go ahead.

212
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:41,840
I've seen this Ritual Altar before.

213
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,200
Arise from the East,

214
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,679
summon the Eastern host,

215
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,200
Eastern troops surge in mighty force!

216
00:11:48,399 --> 00:11:49,559
Swiftly, by decree!

217
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,919
Arise from the South,

218
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:53,600
summon the Southern host,

219
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,600
Southern troops march far and wide!

220
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,679
Swiftly, by decree!

221
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,039
Arise, west wind...

222
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,120
Wait.

223
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,559
Lao Jiugui,

224
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,720
why is this different from ten years ago?

225
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:05,799
Chuanzhong,

226
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:08,519
what I'm summoning for you this time

227
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,360
is far mightier than ten years ago.

228
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,320
Really?

229
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,600
So, shall I summon them or not?

230
00:12:14,679 --> 00:12:15,159
Summon them.

231
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:15,879
Continue.

232
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,679
Arise from the West,

233
00:12:18,679 --> 00:12:19,559
summon the Western host,

234
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:22,039
Western troops descend to the altar!

235
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:23,440
Swiftly, by decree!

236
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:25,840
Arise from the North,

237
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,519
summon the Northern host,

238
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:30,120
Northern troops, heed my command!

239
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,559
Swiftly, by decree!

240
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,519
Obey my command!

241
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:38,919
They're coming now.

242
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,440
One blow of the ox horn,

243
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,600
and the Ghost Soldiers rise.

244
00:12:46,159 --> 00:12:47,279
They're coming, they're coming!
